[1mnew file mode 100644[m
[1mindex 00000000..97c50f40[m
[1m--- /dev/null[m
[1m+++ b/.cursor/rules/wth_structure.mdc[m
[36m@@ -0,0 +1,44 @@[m
[32m+[m[32m---[m
[32m+[m[32mdescription: Canonical header and footer files for Website Talking Heads site structure[m
[32m+[m[32mglobs: "**/*.php"[m
[32m+[m[32malwaysApply: true[m
[32m+[m[32m---[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m- **Exclusions**[m
[32m+[m[32m  - Files in the `whiteboard/` directory are EXCLUDED from this rule[m
[32m+[m[32m  - Pages in `whiteboard/` may use different header/footer files as needed[m
[32m+[m[32m  - Do not enforce canonical header/footer on files matching `whiteboard/**/*.php`[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m- **Canonical Header File**[m
[32m+[m[32m  - The canonical header file is `includes/header25.php`[m
[32m+[m[32m  - All pages MUST use `header25.php` for the site header[m
[32m+[m[32m  - Do NOT use `header2.php`, `header19.php`, `header_b4.php`, or any other header files[m
[32m+[m[32m  - Reference: [header25.php](mdc:includes/header25.php)[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m- **Canonical Footer File**[m
[32m+[m[32m  - The canonical footer file is `includes/footer25.php`[m
[32m+[m[32m  - All pages MUST use `footer25.php` for the site footer[m
[32m+[m[32m  - Do NOT use `footer.php`, `footer2.php`, `footer_b4.php`, or any other footer files[m
[32m+[m[32m  - Reference: [footer25.php](mdc:includes/footer25.php)[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m- **Usage Pattern**[m
[32m+[m[32m  - Include header: `<?php include('includes/header25.php'); ?>` (adjust path for subdirectories)[m
[32m+[m[32m  - Include footer: `<?php include('includes/footer25.php'); ?>` (adjust path for subdirectories)[m
[32m+[m[32m  - Path examples:[m
[32m+[m[32m    - Root level: `includes/header25.php`[m
[32m+[m[32m    - One level deep: `../includes/header25.php`[m
[32m+[m[32m    - Two levels deep: `../../includes/header25.php`[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m- **Migration**[m
[32m+[m[32m  - When updating existing pages, replace any references to:[m
[32m+[m[32m    - `header2.php` ‚Üí `header25.php`[m
[32m+[m[32m    - `header19.php` ‚Üí `header25.php`[m
[32m+[m[32m    - `header_b4.php` ‚Üí `header25.php`[m
[32m+[m[32m    - `footer.php` ‚Üí `footer25.php`[m
[32m+[m[32m    - `footer2.php` ‚Üí `footer25.php`[m
[32m+[m[32m    - `footer_b4.php` ‚Üí `footer25.php`[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m- **Enforcement**[m
[32m+[m[32m  - All new pages MUST use the canonical header and footer files[m
[32m+[m[32m  - When fixing broken includes, always use the canonical files[m
[32m+[m[32m  - Do not create new header or footer variations without explicit approval[m
